-- Lucidus Hires Former Elliott Management Credit Analyst Robbins
-- B y   M a r y   C h i l d s
-- 2013-05-13T21:32:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-13/lucidus-hires-former-elliott-management-credit-analyst-robbins.html
John Robbins, formerly at Elliott
Management Corp., started work today at credit hedge fund
Lucidus Capital Partners LLP.  Robbins joins as a research analyst in the  New York  office,
Simon Meadows, head of business development at Lucidus in
 London , confirmed by e-mail today. He left Elliott Management
earlier this year.  Robbins declined to comment.  Lucidus , the corporate credit
hedge fund founded as a unit of Caxton Associates LLC byDarryl Green and Geoffrey Sherry, has $1.5 billion in notional assets
under management and employs 43 people in London and New York,
Meadows said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mary Childs in New York at 
